originalText.text: I booked an appointment like I was directed to and carved out time from my day for a specific time and no one called me. They sent me confirmation for my booking, but no one called and when I called to ask what happened they said they didn’t know l! very unprofessional.

originalText.text: Needed some last min documents notarized & was told by a member in the community I could come here to get those services. Giving them zero stars because I just learned that it’s against the law to charge more than 2$ dollars per document. I was charged $3 dollars. This speaks volumes about the company and lack of ethics & just downright disrespectful to the community. How can I trust to ever come back? I wouldn’t recommend. Do not spend a dime here. If they can lie about small stuff like this imagine what else they are hiding?
